lled nursing facility snf or within a dialysis center for patients who suffer from end stage renal disease esrd davita health solutions offers a comprehensive care suite that includes house calls meeting patients where they are a physicianled program that provides primary care behavioral health palliative care comprehensive wellness visits and complementary health care services to patients and their caregivers within the patients home smoother transitions back home to families a postacute care program with employed snfists who help patients experience smoother transitions home from a skilled nursing facility so they can spend more quality time with loved ones and may avoid return visits to the hospital a dialysis center as the medical home an integrated kidney care program that treats esrd patients where they spend  hours per week and coordinates their care across doctors and specialists x support and coordinated care a physicianled interdisciplinary clinical care team comprised of physicians nurse practitioners registered nurses behavioral health and palliative care specialists social workers pharmacists and dietitians davita has a history of changing the way that health care is delivered said dr dinesh kumar senior vice president of davita health solutions over  years our comprehensive care programs in the patients home snf and dialysis center have resulted in  percent fewer hospitalizations and a  percent reduction in snf length of stay and readmission rate as a result our patients are able to spend more time at home with their families experiencing lifes great joys to learn more about davita health solutions how it may impact your members or loved ones visit wwwdavitahealthsolutionscom  about davita health solutionsdavita health solutions is a subsidiary of davita inc a fortune  company and leading provider of integrated health and kidney care services davita health solutions offers payors and riskbearing organizations a suite of home and outpatientbased care programs to address the needs of their highrisk medically complex patient populations its programs include physicianled house calls that extend primary care into the home with a heavy focus on palliative care and behavioral health advanced postacute care with employed snfists and integrated kidney care davita health solutions leverages more than  years of experience in managing highrisk patients under atrisk and shared savings arrangements  through its medical group davita currently operates house calls programs that serve more than  patients in five markets in partnership with  independent and employed primary care physicians through its integrated kidney care division davita manages the total care for more than  renal patients of which nearly  are under atrisk arrangements in  markets and several national programs   about davita incdavita inc a fortune ® company is the parent company of davita kidney care and davita medical group davita kidney care is a leading provider of kidney care in the united states delivering dialysis services to patients with chronic kidney failure and end stage renal disease as of march   davita kidney care operated or provided administrative services at  outpatient dialysis centers located in the united states serving approximately  patients the company also operated  outpatient dialysis centers located in  countries outside the united states davita medical group manages and operates medical groups and affiliated physician networks in california colorado florida nevada new mexico pennsylvania and washington in its pursuit to deliver excellentquality health care in a dignified and compassionate manner as of december   davita medical groups teammates employed clinicians and affiliated clinicians provided care for approximately  million patients for more information please visit davitacomabout media contact kate stabrawakatestabrawadavitacom     to view the original version on pr newswire visithttpwwwprnewswirecomnewsreleasesdavitaintroducesd